<template>
  <vue-office-pdf :src="pdf()" />
</template>

<script>
//引入VueOfficePdf组件
import VueOfficePdf from "@vue-office/pdf";
import "@vue-office/excel/lib/index.css";

export default {
  name: "OfficPdf",
  components: {
    VueOfficePdf,
  },
  methods: {
    pdf() {
      return (
        this.$store.state.api +
        "/office?dw=" +
        this.$store.state.DirPath +
        "/" +
        this.$store.state.OfficEword
      );
    },
  },
};
</script>
